{"tid":1956452,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"慎防釣魚post 記住連登仔都是守法好公民","createTime":"2020-04-03T07:39:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-08T08:25:03.000Z","uid":32906,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"c463ba011fd5534655ac98ed6d9d2cb7ae46ff8a","tid":1956452,"uid":32906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T07:39:18.000Z","msg":"例如有人問<br />\n連登仔係咪原諒左黨鐵喇？<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">小妹想試跳閘但好驚</span><br />\n點解黑警仔女到宜家仲係咩事都無？<br />\n點解連儂牆唔見曬？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">記得唔好認真答</span></span><br />\n<br />\n呢類post 都會引到連登仔自爆分享經驗<br />\n自己有用綠卡 跳閘<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">教埋小妹<br />\nxx站無foodpanda<br />\nxx站咁耐都無事</span><br />\n點樣騷擾黑警家庭<br />\nxxx 仲見到有連儂牆<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">上次x點鐘見到有人貼</span><br />\n<br />\n久唔久就有呢d post 出現大家都好易疏忽<br />\n<br />\n相信未來黑警會用埋呢類釣魚post<br />\n咬埋比較隱形既活躍手足 所以開post 講定先"},{"pid":"cb15dbbe9c1eb335b5d3a71f1ddf8381b248f605","tid":1956452,"uid":65187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T07:41:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6dac2e5789594acb542d98003bd3b2083b78a01","tid":1956452,"uid":65187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T07:42:17.000Z","msg":"通常呢d post都推唔起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5678ddfc2a315f3f514654b08ba4d6f9aaa0d66b","tid":1956452,"uid":237300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b6dac2e5789594acb542d98003bd3b2083b78a01","tid":1956452,"uid":65187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T07:42:17.000Z","msg":"通常呢d post都推唔起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T07:43:17.000Z","msg":"係"},{"pid":"866594c7c1844700ba26efc0cd0f01b9b65954f6","tid":1956452,"uid":282075,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b6dac2e5789594acb542d98003bd3b2083b78a01","tid":195645